%20Work%20Better%26quot%3B%20newsletter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20CEO%20Mark%20Read%20sent%20to%20WPP%20employees%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20everyone%20at%20WPP%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EI%20hope%20you%20had%20a%20restful%20holiday%20season%20and%20the%20chance%20to%20recharge%20over%20the%20break.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20I%20wrote%20to%20you%20in%20December%2C%202025%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20year%20of%20opportunity%20for%20WPP%20%E2%80%93%20a%20year%20when%20we%20can%20win%20through%20a%20relentless%20focus%20on%20our%20clients.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20share%20our%20priorities%20for%20the%20next%2012%20months%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20change%20we%20are%20going%20to%20make%20in%20the%20way%20we%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EClients%2C%20creativity%20and%20our%20work%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWPP's%20mission%20is%20to%20deliver%20creative%20transformation%20for%20the%20world's%20leading%20brands.%20This%20means%20not%20only%20producing%20exceptional%20work%20in%20every%20discipline%20of%20modern%20marketing%2C%20but%20helping%20clients%20transform%20how%20they%20operate%20for%20a%20very%20different%20world.%20This%20is%20ever%20more%20true%20of%20our%20largest%20and%20most%20important%20clients%2C%20who%20come%20to%20us%20for%20the%20quality%20of%20what%20we%20do%2C%20the%20breadth%20of%20our%20skills%2C%20and%20our%20ability%20to%20prepare%20them%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWhile%20industry%20mergers%20and%20jostling%20for%20status%20may%20distract%20our%20competitors%2C%20focus%20will%20be%20paramount%20for%20us%20in%202025.%20We%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20stand%20out%20by%20being%20more%20obsessed%20than%20ever%20with%20serving%20our%20clients.%20In%20every%20single%20decision%20we%20make%2C%20we%20should%20ask%20ourselves%20%26quot%3Bhow%20will%20this%20help%20us%20do%20even%20better%20work%20for%20our%20clients%3F%26quot%3B%20Those%20companies%20who%20embrace%20this%20philosophy%20will%20be%20those%20who%20emerge%20on%20top.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ETechnology%2C%20data%20and%20AI%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EDemand%20from%20clients%20for%20creative%20ideas%2C%20effective%20media%20plans%2C%20brilliant%20PR%20campaigns%20and%20outstanding%20design%20remains%20constant%2C%20but%20the%20way%20in%20which%20we%20deliver%20our%20work%20is%20changing%20faster%20than%20I%20have%20ever%20seen.%20That's%20why%20technology%2C%20data%20and%20AI%20are%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20our%20plans%20for%20the%20future%2C%20and%20why%20adoption%20of%20our%20AI-driven%20marketing%20operating%20system%20WPP%20Open%20has%20grown%20so%20quickly.%20Keeping%20up%20that%20momentum%20is%20another%20key%20objective%20for%202025.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWPP%20Open%20helped%20us%20win%20a%20number%20of%202024's%20biggest%20reviews%20and%20we%20are%20going%20to%20increase%20our%20investment%20in%20Open%20this%20year%20to%20build%20on%20the%20success%20it%20has%20brought%20us.%20It%20will%20be%20central%20to%20how%20we%20bring%20an%20integrated%2C%20AI-enabled%20offer%20to%20market%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20producing%20better%20results%20for%20clients%20and%20winning%20more%20than%20our%20fair%20share%20of%20pitches%20in%20the%20year%20ahead.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EA%20culture%20of%20winning%2C%20together%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFinally%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20culture%20of%20our%20company.%20For%20all%20our%20technological%20sophistication%2C%20we%20remain%20a%20people%20business.%20Across%20everything%20we%20do%2C%20our%20success%20still%20relies%20on%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20human%20connection%2C%20creativity%20and%20relationships.%20Teams%20of%20talented%20individuals%2C%20working%20towards%20common%20goals%2C%20are%20what%20drives%20growth%20for%20our%20clients%20and%20our%20agencies.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EI%20believe%20that%20we%20do%20our%20best%20work%20when%20we%20are%20together%20in%20person.%20It's%20easier%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20other%2C%20it's%20a%20better%20way%20to%20mentor%20colleagues%20starting%20out%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20us%20win%20pitches%20as%20a%20truly%20integrated%20team.%20The%20data%20from%20across%20WPP%20agencies%20shows%20that%20higher%20levels%20of%20office%20attendance%20are%20associated%20with%20stronger%20employee%20engagement%2C%20improved%20client%20survey%20scores%20and%20better%20financial%20performance.%20More%20of%20our%20clients%20are%20moving%20in%20this%20direction%20and%20expecting%20it%20of%20the%20teams%20who%20work%20with%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20all%20these%20reasons%2C%20spending%20more%20time%20together%20is%20important%20to%20all%20of%20us%2C%20and%20we%20are%20making%20a%20change%20to%20help%20that%20happen.%20From%20the%20beginning%20of%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20expectation%20across%20WPP%20will%20be%20that%20most%20of%20us%20spend%20an%20average%20of%20four%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20we're%20going%20back%20to%20old%20ways%20of%20doing%20things.%20During%20the%20pandemic%20we%20all%20learned%20the%20value%20of%20greater%20flexibility%20in%20our%20working%20lives%20and%20of%20being%20trusted%20to%20balance%20work%20and%20personal%20commitments.%20We%20need%20to%20keep%20that%20spirit%20of%20flexibility%20and%20trust%2C%20and%20will%20approach%20this%20transition%20with%20pragmatism%20and%20an%20understanding%20of%20people's%20different%20circumstances.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20clear%20process%20to%20request%20additional%20flexibility%20%E2%80%93%20including%20for%20those%20with%20caring%20responsibilities%2C%20health%20issues%20and%20other%20considerations.%20Some%20roles%20that%20have%20always%20been%20fully%20or%20largely%20remote%20will%20continue%20as%20they%20are.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20know%20that%20for%20some%20colleagues%20this%20new%20policy%20will%20require%20adjustments%20to%20their%20routines%20and%20arrangements%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20will%20not%20come%20into%20effect%20until%20April%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20people%20time%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20they%20need%20to.%20There%20is%20also%20work%20to%20do%20between%20now%20and%20April%20to%20ensure%20we%20make%20the%20best%20use%20of%20our%20workspaces.%20Our%20WPP%20campuses%20offer%20superb%20working%20environments%20in%20beautifully%20designed%20buildings%20with%20leading%20environmental%20credentials.%20But%20it%20will%20take%20detailed%20planning%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20to%20address%20capacity%20requirements%20and%20other%20related%20areas%2C%20and%20I'd%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20teams%20who%20are%20already%20hard%20at%20work%20figuring%20that%20out.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EYour%20leaders%20are%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20WPP%20People%20and%20Real%20Estate%20teams%2C%20and%20will%20follow%20up%20with%20next%20steps%20for%20your%20part%20of%20the%20business.%20It's%20important%20that%20we%20take%20a%20consistent%20approach%20across%20our%20agencies%2C%20who%20will%20communicate%20the%20requirements%20to%20you%20in%20detail.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20visit%20insideWPP%20for%20FAQs%2C%20details%20of%20the%20policy%2C%20and%20an%20AI-powered%20chat%20agent%20to%20help%20answer%20your%20questions.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EA%20collaborative%2C%20winning%20culture%20is%20what%20makes%20WPP%20and%20our%20agencies%20a%20great%20place%20to%20work%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20key%20to%20our%20future%20gro