%20is%20its%20opponent%20in%20Delhi%20and%20is%20harbouring%20a%20misconception%20that%20it%20will%20win%20again%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections.%20In%20a%20swift%2C%20stinging%20response%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20remarks%20have%20laid%20bare%20the%20%26quot%3Bsecret%20cooperation%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20Delhi%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20spat%20between%20the%20senior%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20allies%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20AAP%20said%20it%20would%20ask%20other%20members%20to%20remove%20the%20Congress%20from%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20unless%20one%20of%20its%20leaders%2C%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20apologised%20for%20calling%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%26quot%3Banti-national%26quot%3B.%20Even%20then%2C%20the%20AAP%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20doing%20everything%20it%20could%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20helped%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Delhi%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20is%20a%20former%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20AAP)%20are%20our%20opposition.%20They%20are%20harbouring%20a%20misconception%20since%20they%20won%20twice%20(in%20Delhi)...%20the%20voters'%20mood%20seems%20to%20have%20changed%20now.%20The%20Congress%20is%20campaigning%20well%20and%20we%20may%20see%20good%20results%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20clip%20of%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20remarks%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20comments%20have%20proven%20what%20the%20people%20already%20believed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGehlot%20ji%2C%20you%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20Congress%20sees%20the%20AAP%20as%20the%20opposition%20in%20Delhi.%20You%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20BJP.%20People%20also%20felt%20that%20the%20AAP%20is%20the%20opposition%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20its%20partner.%20People%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20fighting%20the%20elections%20together%20against%20the%20AAP.%20So%20far%2C%20this%20cooperation%20between%20you%20two%20was%20a%20secret.%20Today%2C%20you%20have%20made%20it%20public.%20Thank%20you%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%20for%20this%20clarification%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20wrote%20in%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20From%20Allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20-%20another%20key%20INDIA%20ally%20-%20threw%20its%20weight%20behind%20the%20AAP%20for%20the%20Delhi%20polls%2C%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20which%20had%20reportedly%20done%20so%20a%20day%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20its%20President%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20for%20the%20support%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20grateful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTMC%20has%20announced%20support%20to%20AAP%20in%20Delhi%20elections.%20I%20am%20personally%20grateful%20to%20Mamta%20Didi.%20Thank%20you%20Didi.%20U%20have%20always%20supported%20and%20blessed%20us%20in%20our%20good%20and%20bad%20times%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20and%20the%20party's%20leader%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20responded%20almost%20immediately%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20your%20back%20%40AamAadmiParty.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20had%20also%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20INDIA%20ally%20Samajwadi%20Party%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20its%20chief%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20reportedly%20said%20he%20would%20support%20the%20AAP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20very%20much%20Akhilesh%20ji.%20You%20always%20support%20and%20stand%20with%20us.%20I%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20are%20grateful%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20had%20backed%20the%20AAP%20during%20the%202020%20elections%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20will%20vote%20on%20February%205%20and%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20held%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736338380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjh55n3eo_arvind-kejriwal-ashok-gehlot_650x400_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-congress-vs-aap-arvind-kejriwal-hits-back-at-ashok-gehlot-congress-bjp-tie-up-proved-7428070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20widening%20of%20fissures%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%2C%20Congres%20leader%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20has%20said%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20party%20is%20the%20Congress'%20opponent%20in%20Delhi%20and%20is%20harbouring%20a%20misconception%20that%20it%20wi%20win%20again%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-elections-congress-vs-aap-arvind-kejriwal-hits-back-at-ashok-gehlot-congress-bjp-tie-up-proved-7428070%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20one%20cares%20girl...'%3A%20Musk%20brutally%20trolls%20Trudeau%20for%20his%2051st%20state%20remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736338323000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117055942%2Cimgsize-16736.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-calls-justin-trudeau-a-girl-amid-fiery-exchange-over-trumps-canada-takeover-idea%2Farticleshow%2F117055803.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F