tical%20gimmicks%E2%80%9D%2C%20likely%20referring%20to%20a%20two-month%20sales%20tax%20holiday%20and%20C%24250%20rebates%20for%20most%20workers%2C%20underscoring%20the%20fundamental%20problem%20with%20Trudeau's%20brand%20of%20leadership.%20For%20a%20leader%20who%20had%20come%20to%20power%20in%202015%20promising%20%E2%80%9CSunny%20Ways%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20nation%2C%20all%20he%20could%20offer%20in%20the%20end%20was%20political%20gimmickry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20situation%20post-Covid%20has%20been%20debilitating%20for%20most%20Canadians%20and%20his%20management%20of%20Covid%20left%20a%20large%20majority%20unimpressed.%20As%20unemployment%20skyrocketed%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20crisis%20gained%20ground%2C%20Canadians'%20faith%20in%20Trudeau's%20abilities%20kept%20dwindling.%20His%20popularity%20plummeted%20and%20backbenchers%20began%20to%20desert%20him%2C%20fearing%20for%20their%20own%20political%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20foreign%20policy%20front%2C%20Trump's%20election%20victory%20came%20as%20a%20huge%20setback.%20Trump%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20pressure%20over%20tariffs%20led%20to%20Trudeau's%20resignation%3B%20he%20also%20took%20a%20jibe%20at%20Canada's%20situation%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20should%20become%20%E2%80%9Cthe%2051st%20State%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20US.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Canada%20merged%20with%20the%20US%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20Tariffs%2C%20taxes%20would%20go%20way%20down%2C%20and%20they%20would%20be%20TOTALLY%20SECURE%20from%20the%20threat%20of%20the%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20Ships%20that%20are%20constantly%20surrounding%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20rubbing%20salt%20in%20Trudeau's%20wounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Lost%20Decade%20For%20India-Canada%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20India%2C%20Trudeau%20was%20an%20unmitigated%20disaster.%20Canada%2C%20under%20his%20leadership%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20achieve%20the%20unthinkable%3A%20become%20the%20'new%20Pakistan'%20in%20the%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20matrix.%20Trudeau's%20contribution%20to%20the%20fiasco%20that%20is%20the%20current%20India-Canada%20ties%20can't%20be%20overestimated.%20The%20two%20nations%20had%20almost%20succeeded%20in%20moving%20beyond%20the%20Kanishka%20bombings%2C%20the%20nuclear%20challenge%2C%20and%20the%20wider%20Cold%20War%20strategic%20divergence.%20In%20particular%2C%20under%20Stephen%20Harper%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20from%202006%20to%202015%2C%20the%20shift%20in%20tone%20and%20tenor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20substance%20of%20engagement%2C%20became%20pronounced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Trudeau's%20leadership%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20decline%20was%20swift.%20His%20courting%20of%20Khalistani%20extremists%20to%20strengthen%20his%20domestic%20position%20clouded%20his%20ability%20to%20view%20India-Canada%20relations%20with%20the%20seriousness%20they%20deserved.%20By%20focusing%20on%20India%20as%20a%20target%2C%20he%20sought%20to%20rally%20his%20party's%20base%20in%20a%20last-ditch%20effort.%20When%20Trudeau%20claimed%20last%20September%20that%20Canadian%20security%20agencies%20had%20credible%20evidence%20linking%20Indian%20government%20officials%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20few%20in%20India%20took%20his%20assertions%20seriously.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20his%20own%20government%20that%20had%20repeatedly%20refused%20to%20extradite%20Nijjar%20and%20other%20extremists%20despite%20India's%20persistent%20requests%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20hateful%2C%20violent%20rhetoric%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGood%20Riddance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelf-righteous%20posturing%20by%20Trudeau%20and%20his%20party%20has%20been%20aimed%20at%20courting%20a%20key%20electoral%20demographic.%20Yet%2C%20his%20unwillingness%20to%20understand%20Indian%20concerns%20and%20lack%20of%20sensitivity%20about%20Sikh%20separatism%20have%20done%20some%20serious%20damage%20to%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20India-Canada%20ties.%20Trudeau's%20departure%20was%20needed%20for%20an%20India-Canada%20reset%20as%20the%20strategic%20partnership%20that%20was%20put%20in%20place%20in%202015%20now%20lies%20in%20shambles.%20His%20successors%20will%20have%20to%20work%20hard%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20reset%20happens%20quickly%20in%20order%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20lost%20decade%20under%20Trudeau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Harsh%20V%20Pant%20is%20Vice%20President%20for%20Studies%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736337660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmuipn7s_trudeau_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-an-india-canada-reset-trudeau-really-had-to-go-7427961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trudeau's%20departure%20was%20needed%20for%20an%20India-Canada%20reset%20as%20the%20strategic%20partnership%20that%20was%20put%20in%20place%20in%202015%20now%20lies%20in%20shambles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-an-india-canada-reset-trudeau-really-had-to-go-7427961%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pacific%20Palisades%3A%20The%20celebrity%20LA%20area%20ravaged%20by%20wildfire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736337408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F37bf%2Flive%2Fc3f28a30-cd98-11ef-94cb-5f844ceb9e30.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcrmnm2g1z74o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Famous%20faces%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20flee%20the%20usually%20idyllic%20neighbourhood%20as%20a%20massive%20