at%20ultra-processed%20foods%20cause%20weight%20gain.%3Cp%3ENational%20Institute%20of%20Diabetes%20and%20Digestive%20and%20Kidney%20Diseases%2C%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20nutrition%20researcher%20who%20studies%20ultra-processed%20foods%20doesn't%20categorically%20ban%20them%20at%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20relies%20on%20nutrition%20basics%20to%20choose%20snacks%20that%20are%20a%20bit%20healthier%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrioritize%20beans%2C%20whole%20grains%2C%20and%20vegetables%2C%20while%20avoiding%20added%20sugar%20and%20excess%20sodium.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENIH%20scientist%20Kevin%20Hall%20pioneered%20the%20first%20study%20to%20definitively%20prove%20that%20ultra-processed%20foods%20%E2%80%94%20like%20chicken%20tenders%20and%20prepackaged%20snacks%20%E2%80%94%20drive%20us%20to%20overeat%20and%20gain%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%20at%20home%2C%20he%20doesn't%20avoid%20convenience%20food%2C%20and%20buys%20ultra-processed%20snacks%20for%20his%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20says%20his%20strategy%20is%20not%20as%20contradictory%20as%20it%20seems%2C%20if%20you%20understand%20the%20nutrition%20science%20behind%20his%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3cab20b-23c8-4b29-b59d-782a4db398cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20we%20know%20%E2%80%94%20and%20don't%20know%20%E2%80%94%20about%20ultra-processed%20foods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20ago%2C%20Hall%20was%20the%20first%20to%20show%20definitively%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-processed-foods-lead-to-weight-gain-nih-study-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultra-processed%20foods%20cause%20people%20to%20eat%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20food%20(500%20calories%20per%20day!)%20and%20gain%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20big%20deal%3A%20beforehand%2C%20scientists%20could%20only%20draw%20vague%20connections%20between%20ultra-processed%20diets%20and%20long-term%20health%20outcomes.%20There%20wasn't%20a%20definitive%20cause-and-effect%20relationship%20established%20between%20ultra-processed%20foods%20and%20poor%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall's%20team%20at%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health%20put%20people%20into%20a%20laboratory%2C%20gave%20them%20strictly%20prepared%20foods%2C%20and%20studied%20every%20morsel%20they%20digested%20for%20several%20weeks%20at%20a%20time%2C%20seeing%20what%20different%20diets%20did%20to%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20research%20on%20UPFs%20has%20snowballed.%20Today%2C%20ultra-processed%20foods%20are%20the%20poster%20child%20for%20everything%20that's%20wrong%20with%20American%20diets.%20Politicians%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20are%20promising%20to%20weed%20them%20out%20of%20our%20diets%20as%20a%20result%20of%20all%20the%20new%20research%20that%20has%20cropped%20up%20since%20Hall's%20landmark%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a72c54f-cbe5-499d-a096-dd00ebd0db50%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20not%20let%20perfect%20be%20the%20enemy%20of%20good%2C%20Hall%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chicken%20teriyaki%20meal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f5bfaede59ade1a3b515c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltra-processed%3F%20Yep.%20But%20also%20rich%20in%20vegetables%2C%20with%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20fiber%20and%20protein.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20is%20not%20so%20strict%20about%20cutting%20all%20UPFs%20out%2C%20and%20he%20isn't%20going%20to%20tell%20people%20what%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20stand%20on%20my%20soapbox%20to%20claim%20to%20know%20all%20the%20answers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20still%20don't%20know%20exactly%20why%20ultra-processed%20foods%20are%20so%20bad%20for%20us.%20More%20importantly%2C%20he