sider.com%2Fultra-processed-food-expert-tips-for-avoiding-the-worst-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Italian%20Journalist%20and%20Podcaster%20Cecilia%20Sala%20Freed%20by%20Iran%20Following%20%E2%80%98Intensive%E2%80%99%20Diplomatic%20Effort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736336591000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236269571%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prominent%20Italian%20journalist%20and%20podcaster%20Cecilia%20Sala%20has%20been%20freed%20from%20Tehran%E2%80%99s%20Evin%20prison%20for%20political%20prisoners%20where%20she%20had%20been%20detained%20since%20Dec.%2019.%20A%20spokesman%20for%20Italian%20Premiere%20Giorgia%20Meloni%E2%80%99s%20office%20on%20Wed.%20said%20Sala%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20arrested%20while%20reporting%20in%20the%20Iranian%20capital%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20was%20flying%20home%20on%20an%20airplane%20following%20%E2%80%9Cintensive%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Nvivarelli%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLay%20Down%2C%20Water%20Took%20Me%20To%20Safety%26quot%3B%3A%20Survivor%20Of%20Flooded%20Assam%20Mine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20body%20was%20recovered%20and%20eight%20people%20are%20still%20trapped%20after%20water%20gushed%20into%20a%20340-foot%20deep%20'rat-hole'%20mine%20in%20Assam%20and%20flooded%20it%20on%20Monday.%20While%20several%20teams%2C%20including%20one%20from%20the%20Navy%2C%20are%20engaged%20in%20rescue%20operations%2C%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20the%20chances%20of%20the%20remaining%20miners%20being%20rescued%20alive%20are%20slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20who%20were%20in%20the%20mines%20managed%20to%20escape%20and%20some%20others%20were%20fortunate%20not%20to%20be%20working%20the%20shift%20during%20which%20the%20flooding%20occurred%2C%20but%20they%20are%20all%20desperate%20for%20any%20news%20because%20they%20have%20friends%20trapped%20in%20the%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EH%20Islam%20said%20he%20arrived%20in%20Umrangso%20to%20work%20in%20the%20Assam%20Coal%20Quarry%20situated%20in%20the%203%20Kilo%20area%20last%20week%20and%20was%20working%20his%20first%20shift%20on%20Monday%20when%20the%20flooding%20occurred.%20He%20recounted%20hearing%20a%20gush%20of%20water%20and%20people%20shouting%20for%20help.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20practically%20no%20safety%20gear%20and%20got%20lucky%20because%20a%20stream%20of%20water%20carried%20him%20to%20the%20surface.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20work%20around%206.30%20am%20and%2C%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20I%20heard%20people%20shouting.%20I%20called%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20people%20I%20know%2C%20whom%20I%20call%20'%3Cem%3EMama%3C%2Fem%3E'%20and%20told%20him%2C%20'%3Cem%3EMama%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there's%20water.%20run%20quickly%20if%20you%20want%20to%20live'.%20I%20managed%20to%20make%20it%20halfway%20out%20when%20the%20force%20of%20the%20water%20knocked%20me%20down.%20The%20rope%20and%20cloth%20around%20my%20head%20fell...%20We%20had%20no%20helmets%2C%20just%20a%20cloth...%20I%20figured%20that%20the%20flowing%20water%20would%20take%20me%20out%20to%20the%20surface%20and%20I%20lay%20down%2C%20and%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened.%20I%20got%20saved%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20survivor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20worker%2C%20Jalaluddin%2C%20interjected%20and%20said%20no%20safety%20gear%20is%20provided%20to%20them.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20not%20working%20the%20shift%20that%20day%20but%20four%20of%20the%2010%20people%20he%20shares%20a%20room%20with%20did.%20Only%20one%20of%20them%20has%20come%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20conditions%20in%20the%20mine%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20300%20feet%20deep%20and%20then%20there%20are%20many%20tunnels%2C%20which%20are%20linked%20to%20each%20other.%20The%20height%20in%20the%20tunnels%20is%20barely%20three%20feet%2C%20there%20is%20no%20room%20to%20even%20stand%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20bend%20and%20mine%20for%20coal.%20Even%20when%20sitting%2C%20the%20roof%20is%20just%204-5%20inches%20above%20our%20heads.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDivers%20On%20The%20Job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20said%20the%20Navy%20team%20that%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation%20includes%20clearance%20divers%20trained%20in%20deep-depth%20diving%20and%20recovery%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20more%20de-watering%20pumps%20are%20being%20sent%20to%20the%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rescue%20operation%20is%20in%20full%20swing%20with%20Army%20and%20NDRF%20divers%20having%20already%20entered%20the%20well.%20Navy%20personnel%20are%20on-site%2C%20making%20final%20preparations%20to%20dive%20in%20after%20them.%20Meanwhile%2C%20State%20Disaster%20Rescue%20Force%20(SDRF)%20de-watering%20pumps%20have%20departed%20from%20Umrangshu%20for%20the%20location.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20ONGC%20de-watering%20pump%20has%20been%20loaded%20onto%20an%20MI-17%20helicopter%20at%20Kumbhigram%2C%20awaiting%20weather%20clearance%20for%20deployment%2C%26quot%3B%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736336520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fi68o8gj8_assam-mine-rescue_625x300_08_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frun-if-you-want-to-live-survivor-on-moment-water-flooded-assam-rat-hole-mine-7427620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20body%20was%20recovered%20and%20eight%20other%20people%20are%20still%20trapped%20after%20water%20gushed%20into%20a%20340-foot%20deep%20'rat-hole'%20mine%20in%20Assam%20and%20flooded%20it%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frun-if-you-want-to-live-sur