the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrgmAKNhVeG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FrgmAKNhVeG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1876647947347345565%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTejas%2C%20we%20started%20inducting%20it%20in%202016...We%20should%20go%20back%20to%201984%20when%20the%20project%20was%20conceived.%20The%20aircraft%20flew%2017%20years%20later%20in%202001.%20Then%2C%20the%20induction%20started%20another%2016%20years%20later%20in%202016.%20Today%20we%20are%20in%202024%20and%20I%20(Indian%20Air%20Force)%20do%20not%20have%20the%20first%2040%20aircraft...This%20is%20the%20production%20capability.%20We%20need%20to%20do%20something%20and%20I'm%20very%20convinced%20that%20we%20need%20to%20have%20competition%2C%20we%20need%20to%20have%20multiple%20sources%20available%20so%20that%20people%20are%20wary%20of%20losing%20their%20orders%2C%20otherwise%2C%20things%20won't%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(LCA)%20programme%20was%20envisioned%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20to%20replace%20the%20MiG-21%20and%20Su-7%20fleet.%20The%20programme%20got%20a%20boost%20in%20the%20late%2090s%20and%20on%20January%204%2C%202001%2C%20the%20Technology%20Demonstrator-1%20(TD-1)%20version%20of%20the%20LCA%20was%20airborne%20and%20rechristened%20'Tejas'%2C%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-new-tejas-fighter-jet-variant-is-different-from-its-predecessor-5685154%5C%22%3EThe%20Second%20Series%20Production%20(SP2)%20Tejas%20aircraft%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20given%20initial%20operational%20clearance%20in%202016.%20The%20Tejas%20Mk1%20version%20was%20inducted%20in%20the%20Air%20Force's%20No.%2045%20Squadron%20-%20'The%20Flying%20Daggers'.%20Later%2C%20another%20Tejas%20squadron%2C%20the%20No.%2018%20Squadron%20-%20'The%20Flying%20Bullets'%20began%20operating%20the%20Mk1%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tejas%20fighter%20jet%20is%20manufactured%20by%20the%20Bengaluru-headquartered%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%20(HAL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACM%20AP%20Singh%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20private%20players%20in%20defence%20manufacturing%20and%20production%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BR%26amp%3BD%20loses%20its%20relevance%20if%20it%20is%20not%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20timeline.%20Time%20is%20a%20very%20important%20thing.%20We%20need%20to%20give%20greater%20leeway%20to%20the%20researchers.%20There%20will%20be%20failures%2C%20let's%20not%20be%20scared%20of%20failures.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20losing%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20because%20we%20are%20scared%20of%20failure...Defence%20is%20one%20sector%20where%20time%20is%20very%20important.%20If%20we%20don't%20meet%20the%20timeline%2C%20technology%20is%20of%20no%20use.%20So%20we%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20our%20failures%2C%20move%20on%20and%20not%20be%20scared%20of%20those%20failures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BR%26amp%3BD%20funds%20are%20woefully%20short.%20We%20are%20just%20about%20at%205%25%2C%20and%20it%20should%20be%20at%2015%25%20(of%20the%20defence%20budget).%20We%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20these%20funds%20are%20increased%20and%20they%20are%20available%20to%20private%20players%20also...We%20need%20to%20increase%20the%20schemes%20to%20have%20more%20private%20players%2C%20and%20maybe%20have%20a%20competitive%20approach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina's%206th%20Gen%20Fighter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20chief's%20concerns%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20Tejas'%20procurement%20comes%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-flies-brand-new-stealth-fighter-jet-believed-to-be-6th-generation-7336128%5C%22%3EChina's%20development%20of%20its%20'6th%20Generation%3C%2Fa%3E%20stealth%20fighter%20jet'%20and%20its%20recent%20trials%20that%20took%20the%20internet%20by%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20defence%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20concerns%20from%20our%20northern%20and%20western%20adversaries.%20Both%20of%20them%20are%20increasing%20their%20forces%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20As%20far%20as%20China%20is%20concerned%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20numbers.%20The%20technology%20is%20also%20growing%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20We%20just%20saw%20the%20flight%20of%20the%20latest%20new%20generation%20aircraft%20that%20they%20have%20pulled%20out..%20the%20stealth%20fighter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20the%20second%20country%20in%20the%20world%20after%20the%20US%20to%20have%20at%20least%20two%20types%20of%20stealth%20fighter%20jets%20--%20J-20%20and%20J-35%20--%20have%20been%20developed%20in%20China%20in%20record%20time.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20so-called%206th%20generation%20fighter%20is%20up%20for%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'2025%20-%20The%20Year%20Of%20Reforms'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20has%20declared%202025%20as%20the%20'year%20of%20reforms'.%20With%20an%20%26quot%3Baim%20to%20further%20bolster%20Jointness%20%26amp%3B%20Integration%20initiatives%20and%20facilitate%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Integrated%20Theatre%20Commands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D2089184%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520order%2520to%2520give%2520impetus%2Cof%2520multi%252Ddomain%2520integrated%2520operations.%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAcquisition%20procedures%20need%20to%20be%20made%20simpler%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20time-sensitive%20to%20facilitate%20swifter%20and%20robust%20capability%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFacilitate%20technology%20transfer%20and%20knowledge%20sharing%20between%20the%20defence%20sector%20and%20civil%20industries%2C%20promoting%20public-private%20partnerships%20by%20improving%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BPosition%20India%20as%20a%20credible%20exporter%20of%20defence%20products%2C%20fostering%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20partnerships%20between%20Indian%20industries%20and%20foreign%20Original%20Equipment%20Manufacturers%20for%20knowledge%20sharing%20%26amp%3B%20resource%20integration%2C%26quot%3B%20are%20among%20several%20areas%20for%20focussed%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGE%20F404%20Engine%20Delay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20has%20ordered%2083%20Tejas%20Mk1A%20variants%20in%20a%20Rs%2036%2C468%20crore%20deal%20with%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited.%20In%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Council%20cleared%20the%20project%20to%20acquire%2097%20more%20Tejas%20jets%20for%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20The%20Tejas%20fighter%20jets%20will%20be%20powered%20by%20US-made%20General%20Electric's%20F404%20fighter%20jet%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tejas%20MK1A%20variant%2C%20the%20advanced%20version%20of%20the%20MK1%2C%20which%20is%20already%20operational%20in%20two%20squadrons%2C%20took%20to%20the%20skies%20on%20March%2028%20last%20year%20for%20a%20historic%20test%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20force%20plans%20to%20raise%20the%20first%20squadron%20of%20the%20indigenous%20LCA%20Mark%201A%20fighter%20aircraft%20squadron%20at%20the%20Nal%20air%20base%20in%20the%20Bikaner%20district%20of%20Rajasthan%20near%20the%20Pakistan%20front.%20The%20Tejas%20will%20replace%20one%20of%20the%20two%20MiG-21%20squadrons%20already%20stationed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20variants%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20delivered%20by%20July%20but%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Flag-in-us-engine-supply-delays-iaf-induction-of-tejas-mark-1a%2Farticleshow%2F114748534.cms%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20October%20last%20year%20said%20that%20the%20HAL%20will%20be%20able%20to%20deliver%20only%20two%20to%20three%20Tejas%20MK1A%20instead%20of%20the%2016%20promised%20to%20the%20IAF%20in%20the%202024-2025%20fiscal%20under%20the%20deal%20to%20procure%2083-such%20fighter%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20have%20flagged%20the%20delay%20in%20delivery%20of%2099%20GE%20F404%20engines%20during%20their%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20and%20GE%20has%20promised%20to%20begin%20supply%20by%20March%202025%2C%20already%20two%20years%20behind%20the%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdefence-india-imposes-penalties-on-ge-aerospace-amid-delays-in-tejas-engine-deliveries-3655964%2F%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20imposed%20penalties%20on%20GE%20Aerospace%20over%20the%20two-year%20deal.%20The%20first%20timeline%20to%20deliver%20the%20engines%20was%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20with%20our%20partner%20HAL%20and%20suppliers%20to%20resolve%20constraints%20and%20deliver%20F404-IN20%20engines%20for%20the%20LCA%20Mk1%20programme%2C%26quot%3B%20Financial%20Express%20reported%2C%20quoting%20GE%20Aerospace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejas%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20multi-role%20fighters%20of%20its%20weight%20and%20class%20and%20has%20an%20impeccable%20safety%20record%20since%20its%20first%20flight%20in%202001.%20The%204.5%20generation%20aircraft%20can%20be%20used%20for%20multiple%20roles%20like%20ground%20attack%2C%20interception%2C%20air-to-air%20combat%20and%20air%20defence.%20Nigeria%2C%20Philippines%2C%20Argentina%20and%20Egypt%20have%20shown%20interest%20in%20procuring%20indigenously-developed%20Tejas%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFalling%20Squadron%20Strength%20-%20A%20Cause%20Of%20Concern%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-two%20is%20the%20sanctioned%20squadron%20strength%20for%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20but%20currently%2C%20only%2031%20are%20active.%20A%20fighter%20squadron%20has%20typically%2018%20aircraft%20including%20two%20trainer%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Demand%20for%20Grants%202024-2025'%20report%20on%20defence%20flagged%20the%20shortage%20of%20fighter%20aircraft%20in%20the%20air%20force%20and%20said%20the%20IAF%20needs%20at%20least%20180%20fighter%20jets%20under%20the%20present%20circumstances.%20The%20strength%20may%20further%20deplete%20after%20the%20phasing%20out%20of%20the%20ageing%20MiG-21%20which%20has%20been%20in%20service%20since%201963%20and%20has%20undergone%20multiple%20overhauls%20over%2060%20years.%20The%20MiG-29s%2C%20SEPECAT%20Jaguars%2C%20and%20Mirage-2000s%20are%20other%20aircraft%20procured%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20(falling%20squadron%20strength)%20will%20be%20addressed%20in%20the%20long%20run%20by%20the%20timely%20induction%20of%20Multi-Role%20Fighter%20Aircraft%20(MRFA)%20and%20LCA%20Mark%20II.%20Critical%20combat%20enablers%20like%20the%20airborne%20early%20warning%20aircraft%2C%20flight%20refuellers%20and%20special%20electronic%20intelligence%20and%20surveillance%20are%20an%20integral%20element%20of%20modern-day%20combat%2C%26quot%3B%20PTI%20reported%2C%20quoting%20an%20IAF%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Defence%20noted%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20delay%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20light%20combat%20aircraft%20from%20HAL.%20The%20Committee%20recommended%20that%20if%20there%20are%20delays%20in%20the%20indigenous%20manufacture%20of%20multi-role%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20the%20government%20should%20consider%20the%20counter-purchase%20of%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20the%20capital%20funding%20provided%20to%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20was%20insufficient%20to%20buy%20a%20large%20number%20of%20fighter%20jets%20and%20suggested%20that%20procurement%20should%20not%20be%20delayed%20due%20to%20inadequate%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736335800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-10%2Ftejas-fighter-jet_650x400_41475985600.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffirst-40-tejas-still-not-air-force-chief-air-chief-marshal-ap-singh-as-china-tests-6th-gen-jets-7427692%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20of%20Air%20Staff%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20AP%20Singh%2C%20flagged%20delays%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20the%20Tejas%20fighter%20aircraft%20into%20service%2C%20calling%20for%20increased%20private%20partnership%20in%20developing%20defence%20products%20and%20providing%20more%20funds%20for%20Research%20and%20Development%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffirst-40-tejas-still-not-air-force-chief-air-chief-marshal-ap-singh-as-china-tests-6th-gen-jets-7427692%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20'calls'%20Canada's%20outgoing%20PM%20Trudeau%3A%20Girl%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20the%20....%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736335576000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117054619%2Cimgsize-24490.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-calls-canadas-former-pm-justin-trudeau-girl-youre-not-the-%2Farticleshow%2F117054636.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20addressed%20outgoing%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20highlighting%20Trudeau%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20governor%20of%20Canada.%20This%20was%20in%20response%20to%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20statement%20affirming%20that%20Canada%20will%20never%20become%20part%20of%20the%20US.%20