m%20and%20was%20told%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-moved-to-canada-not-perfect-but-prefer-over-us-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20heard%20about%20someone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-tips-moving-abroad-with-kids-living-overseas-family-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelocating%20to%20a%20new%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20dreamed%20of%20doing%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20biochemistry%20at%20university%20and%20completed%20a%20postgraduate%20program%20in%20computer%20science.%20I%20worked%20in%20IT%20for%20around%2012%20years%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20where%20I%20gained%20experience%20in%20computer%20engineering%2C%20billing%20administration%2C%20and%20team%20management%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20desire%20to%20relocate%20heavily%20influenced%20my%20life.%20When%20I%20courted%20my%20wife%2C%20I%20told%20her%20about%20my%20dream%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20it%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20for%20her.%20I%20started%20getting%20myself%20ready%20to%20move%20by%20gaining%20IT%20certifications%20through%20a%20Canadian%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-us-to-canada-help-have-another-baby-after-cancer-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20to%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20after%20successfully%20applying%20for%20permanent%20residency%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20ended%20up%20taking%20me%20around%20nine%20months%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-youre-not-getting-hired-job-interview-resume-advice-tips-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efind%20a%20professional%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20struggled%20to%20get%20my%20foot%20in%20the%20door%20and%20provide%20for%20my%20family's%20basic%20needs.%20I%20feel%20I%20was%20overlooked%20because%20I%20didn't%20have%20Canadian%20work%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f74a3a5-3e0b-443f-9835-5996e8ffe249%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20applied%20for%20professional%20jobs%20in%20Canada%20but%20didn't%20hear%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20arrived%20in%20Canada%20in%202012%20and%20stayed%20with%20my%20sister%2C%20who%20had%20moved%20there%20ahead%20of%20me%2C%20for%20two%20months%20before%20we%20got%20an%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20worked%20in%20a%20bank%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20but%20when%20we%20moved%20she%20decided%20to%20pursue%20her%20hobby%20of%20making%20clothes%2C%20so%20she%20went%20back%20to%20school%20to%20go%20into%20fashion%20design.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffind-job-searching-hunt-tips-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20job-hunting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20for%20professional%20jobs%2C%20such%20as%20analyst%20and%20project%20manager%20positions%2C%20but%20it%20mostly%20was%20crickets.%20I%20wasn't%20hearing%20anything%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeers%20who%20were%20also%20immigrants%20asked%20to%20look%20at%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20I'd%20put%20Nigeria%20all%20over%20the%20place%2C%20someone%20suggested%20I%20remove%20it.%20When%20I%20did%2C%20I%20started%20getting%20follow-up%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20I%20wasn't%20getting%20opportunities%20because%20of%20my%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-name-resume-hired-guilty-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanadian%20work%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Recruiters%20didn't%20say%20it%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20subtle.%20In%20phone%20conversations%2C%20recruiters%20would%20ask%20where%20my%20experience%20was%20based.%20I'd%20explain%20it%20wasn't%20in%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20conversation%20would%20continue%2C%20but%20they'd%20never%20get%20back%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20glaring%