ents%20had%20not%20made%20her%20go%20through%20any%20psychological%20counselling%20or%20treatment%2C%20but%20only%20kept%20her%20on%20medication%20since%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20medical%20board's%20report%20said%20there%20were%20no%20abnormalities%20or%20anomalies%20in%20the%20foetus%20and%20the%20woman%20was%20medically%20fit%20for%20continuation%20of%20the%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20however%2C%20also%20said%20that%20termination%20of%20the%20pregnancy%20could%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20government%20pleader%20Prachi%20Tatke%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20consent%20of%20the%20pregnant%20woman%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance%20in%20such%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20took%20note%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20medical%20board%20report%20has%20clearly%20stated%20the%20woman%20is%20not%20mentally%20disabled%20or%20of%20an%20unsound%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20observation%20(in%20the%20report)%20is%20that%20she%20has%20below%20average%20intelligence.%20Nobody%20can%20be%20super%20intelligent.%20We%20are%20all%20human%20beings%20and%20everybody%20has%20different%20levels%20of%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20she%20has%20below%20average%20intelligence%2C%20does%20she%20have%20no%20right%20to%20be%20a%20mother%3F%20If%20we%20say%20that%20persons%20with%20below%20average%20intelligence%20do%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20be%20parents%2C%20it%20would%20be%20against%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20provisions%20of%20the%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20Act%2C%20a%20pregnancy%20beyond%20the%2020-week%20gestation%20period%20is%20allowed%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20woman%20is%20mentally%20ill%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBorderline%20case%20cannot%20be%20said%20to%20be%20a%20mental%20disorder.%20She%20(the%20pregnant%20woman%20in%20the%20present%20case)%20has%20not%20been%20declared%20as%20mentally%20ill.%20It%20is%20only%20a%20borderline%20case%20of%20intellectual%20functioning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advocate%20of%20the%20petitioner%20informed%20the%20HC%20that%20the%20woman%20has%20now%20disclosed%20to%20her%20parents%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20man%20with%20whom%20she%20is%20in%20a%20relationship%20and%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20asked%20the%20woman's%20parents%20to%20meet%20the%20man%20and%20interact%20with%20him%20to%20see%20if%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20marry%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20parents%2C%20take%20the%20initiative%20and%20talk%20to%20the%20man.%20They%20are%20both%20adults.%20It%20is%20not%20an%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20adopted%20the%20woman%20when%20she%20was%20five-month-old%20infant%2C%20and%20must%20now%20do%20their%20duty%20as%20parents%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20further%20hearing%20on%20January%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736332440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fb2bmik7k_pregnancy-generic-pregnant-generic-pixabay_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjust-because-woman-below-average-intelligence-court-on-abortion-plea-7427279%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20questioned%20whether%20a%20woman%20with%20intellectual%20disability%20has%20no%20right%20to%20become%20a%20mother.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjust-because-woman-below-average-intelligence-court-on-abortion-plea