es%20to%20take%20good%20care%20of%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShegaon%20health%20officer%20Dr%20Deepali%20Rahekar%20was%20part%20of%20the%20health%20team%20that%20visited%20the%20village.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20due%20to%20polluted%20water.%20We%20have%20collected%20samples%20and%20will%20test%20them%20to%20reach%20a%20conclusion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736332440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fje8hhr8g_buldhana-hair-fall_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbald-within-a-week-mass-hair-loss-at-3-maharashtra-villages-sparks-panic-7427269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20residents%20of%20three%20villages%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Buldhana%20district%20have%20turned%20bald%20within%20a%20week%20after%20mass%20hair%20loss%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20Health%20officials%20suspect%20that%20water%20pollution%20due%20to%20fertilisers%20was%20behind%20the%20mass%20hair%20loss%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbald-within-a-week-mass-hair-loss-at-3-maharashtra-villages-sparks-panic-7427269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Spin%20Troubles%20To%20Dressing%20Room%20Leaks%3A%20What%20Indian%20Cricket%20Must%20Lose%20In%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fuv5ksbfg_cricket_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%202024%20a%20satisfactory%20year%20for%20Indian%20men's%20cricket%3F%20That's%20a%20tough%20one%20to%20answer.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20a%20year%20in%20which%20the%20team%20became%20T20I%20world%20champions%20after%2017%20years%20and%20also%20dominated%20the%20shortest%20format%20(24%20wins%20in%2026%20games).%20But%20it%20was%20also%20a%20year%20of%20historic%20lows%20in%20both%20Test%20and%20ODI%20cricket.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%2045%20years%2C%20India%20couldn't%20register%20a%20single%20win%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20in%20a%20calendar%20year%2C%20albeit%20they%20played%20only%20three%20ODIs%20(vs%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20one%20match%20ended%20in%20a%20tie).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memory%20that%20is%20the%20freshest%20in%20our%20minds%20is%20that%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%2C%20which%20rounded%20off%20a%20rather%20disappointing%20year.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20had%20begun%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20promise%20with%20a%20historic%20win%20in%20Cape%20Town.%20India%20had%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20trophy%20to%20the%20Aussies%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20decade.%20Overall%2C%202024%20was%20a%20year%20that%20exposed%20some%20rather%20large%20chinks%20in%20India's%20Test%20armour.%20India%20won%20only%20one%20of%20their%20last%20seven%20Tests%20last%20year.%20That%20is%20not%20a%20statistic%20any%20top%20team%20would%20like%20to%20claim.%20Losing%20a%20three-match%20Test%20series%20at%20home%200-3%20for%20the%20first%20time%20was%20a%20real%20body%20blow.%20As%20former%20India%20captain%20Anjum%20Chopra%20told%20me%20during%20a%20chat%20recently%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20be%20a%20bitter%20pill%20to%20swallow%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20because%20losing%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20but%20not%20being%20in%20the%20contest%20is%20another%20thing%20altogether.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Subpar%20Year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Not%20being%20in%20the%20contest'%20is%20a%20great%20way%20of%20summarising%20Team%20India's%20forgettable%20performances%20in%20both%20ODI%20and%20Test%20cricket%20in%20the%20year%20gone%20by.%20There%20were%20some%20highs%2C%20of%20course%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Test%20wins%20in%20Cape%20Town%20and%20Perth%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20heroics%20in%20Australia%2C%20his%20being%20crowned%20the%20most%20successful%20Indian%20Test%20bowler%20on%20Australian%20soil%20and%20finishing%20the%20year%20with%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20wickets%20across%20all%20teams%20and%20formats.%20Likewise%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20finished%20as%20the%20second-highest%20Test%20run-getter%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20averaged%20over%2052%20in%20ODIs.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%202024%20was%20a%20subpar%20year%20for%20Indian%20ODI%20and%20Test%20cricket.%20So%2C%20what%20are%20the%20big%20lessons%20that%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20should%20learn%20in%202025%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20ODI%20assignment%20of%20the%20year%20will%20be%20against%20England%2C%20at%20home.%20It's%20a%20three-match%20series%20and%20will%20be%20the%20perfect%20platform%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20to%20test%20new%20strategies%20and%20attack%20plans.%20One%20concern%20that's%20common%20to%20both%20the%20ODI%20and%20Test%20arenas%20is%20the%20top-order%20batting%20form.%20If%20you%20ask%20experts%20about%20what's%20the%20biggest%20kryptonite%20hurting%20Indian%20batters%2C%20the%20answer%20will%20be%2C%20their%20vulnerability%20against%20left-arm%20spin%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20and%20quality%20spin%2C%20overall.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20the%20coaching%20staff%20should%20be%20addressing%20on%20a%20war%20footing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Practice%20Issue%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sri%20Lanka%20last%20year%2C%20left-arm%20spinner%20Dunith%20Wellalage%20ran%20through%20the%20Indian%20batting%20line-up%20like%20a%20hot%20knife%20through%20butter.%20Leggie%20Jeffrey%20Vandersay%20topped%20the%20wickets'%20list%20and%20Kamindu%20Mendis%20tried%20to%20fox%20the%20Indian%20batters%20with%20his%20ambidextrous%20bowling%20skills%20(in%20a%20T20I).%20Team%20India%20hit%20a%20new%20low%20when%20they%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%20138%20in%2026.1%20overs%20in%20the%20third%20ODI%2C%20with%20the%20spinners%20taking%20nine%20of%20the%2010%20wickets.%20India's%20problems%20with%20tackling%20spin%20are%20not%20a%20new%20headache%2C%20but%20the%20ODI%20series%20against%20the%20Lankans%20was%20a%20wake-up%20call.%20That%20turned%20into%20a%20blood-curdling%20scream%20when%20left-arm%20spinners%20Ajaz%20Patel%20and%20Mitchell%20Santner%20took%2028%20wickets%20between%20them%20to%20break%20the%20back%20of%20the%20famed%20Indian%20batting%20line-up%2C%20and%20that%20too%20on%20Indian%20pitches.%20Even%20part-timer%20Glenn%20Phillips%20took%20eight%20wickets.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20a%20left-arm%20spinner%20troubling%20Indian%20batters%20was%20not%20a%20common%20occurrence.%20Yes%2C%20there%20was%20someone%20like%20Monty%20Panesar%20who%20troubled%20even%20the%20likes%20of%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20and%20Virender%20Sehwag%20during%20England's%20Test%20series%20win%20in%20India%20in%202012%2C%20but%20that%20was%20a%20one-off.%20Now%2C%20things%20have%20changed%20and%20the%20team%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20tangle%20they%20are%20not%20able%20to%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20view%20that%20since%20most%20batters%20these%20days%20play%20and%20practise%20more%20for%20T20%20cricket%2C%20it%20has%20affected%20their%20ability%20to%20play%20spin.%20Batters%20go%20at%20the%20ball%20with%20harder%20hands%2C%20resulting%20in%20more%20edges.%20Also%2C%20with%20the%20DRS%20around%2C%20defending%20with%20pads%20is%20now%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20You%20now%20see%20Indian%20batters%20being%20foxed%20while%20attempting%20a%20defensive%20shot%20against%20a%20ball%20that%20is%20turning%20away.%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%2C%20arguably%20one%20of%20the%20most%20technically%20adept%20batters%20ever%20in%20world%20cricket%2C%20put%20the%20Indian%20batters'%20struggles%20against%20spin%20down%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20deficiencies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELook%20For%20A%20Lasting%20Fix%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20feel%20that%20India%20should%20stop%20producing%20pitches%20that%20are%20rank%20turners%20for%20home%20series.%20While%20that%20might%20be%20a%20stop-gap%20solution%2C%20it%20can't%20be%20a%20long-term%20fix.%20Don't%20the%20Aussies%2C%20Proteas%20and%20the%20English%20welcome%20visiting%20teams%20with%20spicy%20pitches%2C%20even%20though%20drop-in%20pitches%20have%20somewhat%20dulled%20the%20bite%3F%20The%20solution%20to%20this%20problem%20is%20right%20here%2C%20at%20home%3A%20domestic%20cricket.%20Why%20can't%20our%20%E2%80%98star'%20batters%20play%20Ranji%20Trophy%20cricket%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20are%20not%20in%20form%3F%20(For%20that%20to%20happen%20though%2C%20the%20selectors%20and%20team%20management%20also%20have%20to%20take%20tough%20calls)%20Why%20can't%20an%20underperforming%20batter%20be%20dropped%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20series%3F%20Or%20even%20after%20a%20disastrous%20one%3F%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%2C%20after%20all%2C%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Sydney%20Test.%20We%20didn't%20see%20the%20Aussies%20hesitate%20in%20dropping%20Mitchell%20Marsh%E2%80%94someone%20who%20won%20the%20Allan%20Border%20medal%20for%20being%20the%20best%20Aussie%20cricketer%20in%202023%E2%80%94for%20the%20last%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20India's%20tracks%20where%20domestic%20cricket%20is%20played%20are%20spin%20havens%20and%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20quality%20spinners%20in%20domestic%20teams.%20The%20best%20way%20for%20a%20batter%20to%20fix%20their%20technical%20issues%20is%20to%20actually%20play%20more%20cricket%20against%20opposition%2C%20something%20that%20will%20continually%20address%20their%20weaknesses%2C%20rather%20than%20face%20throw-downs%20or%20net%20bowlers%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20during%20team%20practice%20sessions.%20It's%20high%20time%20our%20superstars%20realised%20that%20going%20back%20to%20domestic%20cricket%20is%20not%20a%20step%20back%20but%20a%20wise%20call%20to%20make.%20Will%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20the%20BCCI%20crack%20the%20whip%20on%20this%20one%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver-Dependent%20On%20Bumrah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20bowling%20department%2C%20the%20biggest%20worry%2C%20especially%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20is%20the%20over-dependence%20on%20Bumrah.%20There's%20no%20point%20being%20in%20denial%20about%20this%20one.%20Bumrah%20is%20a%20once-in-a-generation%20kind%20of%20talent.%20Sure%2C%20when%20he%20rocks%20the%20opposition%20single-handedly%20and%20swings%20the%20momentum%20towards%20his%20team%2C%20it's%20fascinating.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20we%20have%20come%20to%20expect%20nothing%20less%20from%20this%20magician.%20But%20surely%20he%20can't%20be%20the%20only%20one%20winning%20matches%20for%20India.%20I%20also%20hope%20someone%20is%20tracking%20his%20workload%20very%2C%20very%20closely.%20Bumrah%20walking%20off%20the%20ground%20with%20an%20injury%20or%20niggle%20is%20not%20something%20any%20cricket%20fan%20would%20want%20to%20see%20again.%20Now%20there's%20talk%20of%20him%20being%20made%20ODI%20vice-captain%20as%20well.%20The%20selectors%20need%20to%20keep%20looking%20for%20and%20giving%20chances%20to%20new%20fast-bowling%20talent%2C%20as%20they%20did%20with%20Harshit%20Rana%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20aspect%20of%20India's%20bowling%20problems%2C%20especially%20while%20playing%20in%20SENA%20countries%2C%20is%20playing%20another%20out-and-out%20specialist%20fast%20bowler%E2%80%94a%20proper%20wicket-taking%20option%E2%80%94in%20the%20first%20XI.%20This%20is%20possible%20only%20if%20the%20team%20is%20confident%20enough%20to%20drop%20a%20batter%20or%20all-rounder.%20Mohammed%20Shami%20hopefully%20will%20be%20fit%20soon%20and%20cleared%20to%20play%20international%20cricket.%20But%20for%20the%20long%20term%2C%20Rana%2C%20Akash%20Deep%20and%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20should%20be%20backed%20to%20the%20hilt%2C%20and%20new%20talent%20should%20be%20explored.%20This%20will%20also%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20reduce%20the%20burden%20on%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coach%20should%20have%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20how%20he%20wants%20to%20tackle%20big-name%20batters%20and%20their%20own%20individual%20styles%20of%20play.%20Case%20in%20point%3A%20Rishabh%20Pant.%20Does%20Gambhir%20allow%20him%20to%20be%20who%20he%20is%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20many%20times%20a%20completely%20out-of-textbook%20shot%20results%20in%20his%20dismissal%3F%20Or%20does%20he%20curb%20his%20natural%20instincts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20former%20players%20say%20that%20another%20thing%20that%20is%20doing%20no%20good%20is%20leaked%20information.%20The%20last%20thing%20Indian%20cricket%20needs%20right%20now%20is%20news%20of%20%E2%80%98a%20divided%20dressing%20room'%20making%20headlines.%20There%20are%20problems%2C%20yes.%20There%20are%20egos%2C%20yes.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20something%20like%20this%20has%20happened%20to%20a%20proud%20cricket%20team.%20These%20are%20professional%20athletes%20and%20they%20know%20exactly%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%20It's%20just%20a%20question%20of%20putting%20in%20the%20hard%20yards.%20How%20they%20do%20that%20and%20what%20the%20differences%20are%20shouldn't%20be%20public.%20Please%2C%20stop%20the%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736332440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Foh1p966_cricket_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fspin-weakness-to-dressing-room-leaks-what-indian-cricket-must-lose-in-2025-7427278%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20fact%20remains%20that%202024%20was%20a%20sub-par%20year%20for%20Indian%20ODI%20and