sday%2C%20as%20hurricane-force%20winds%20tore%20through%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrightened%20residents%20abandoned%20their%20cars%20on%20one%20of%20the%20only%20roads%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20upscale%20Pacific%20Palisades%20area%2C%20fleeing%20on%20foot%20from%20the%20almost%203%2C000-acre%20(1%2C200-hectare)%20blaze%20engulfing%20an%20area%20packed%20with%20multimillion-dollar%20homes%20in%20the%20Santa%20Monica%20Mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirefighters%20used%20bulldozers%20to%20push%20dozens%20of%20vehicles%20--%20including%20expensive%20models%20like%20BMWs%2C%20Teslas%20and%20Mercedes%20--%20to%20one%20side%2C%20leaving%20many%20crumpled%20and%20with%20their%20alarms%20blaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20Fire%20Department%20Chief%20Kristin%20Crowley%20said%20despite%20the%20chaotic%20evacuation%2C%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20reports%20of%20any%20deaths%20or%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20firefighters%20swarmed%20the%20area%2C%20attacking%20the%20blaze%20from%20the%20ground%20and%20from%20the%20air%2C%20while%20crews%20worked%20in%20steep%20terrain%20to%20cut%20back%20vegetation%20and%20create%20firebreaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2030%2C000%20people%20were%20ordered%20to%20evacuate%20the%20fast-spreading%20flames%2C%20which%20leveled%20multiple%20homes%20as%20powerful%20winds%20spread%20embers%20far%20and%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20out%20of%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Fire%20Chief%20Anthony%20Marrone%2C%20speaking%20at%20an%20afternoon%20press%20conference%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20winds%20are%20expected%20to%20pick%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20town%2C%20on%20the%20northern%20edge%20of%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20another%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20Eaton%20Canyon%2C%20near%20Pasadena%2C%20quickly%20consuming%20200%20acres%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20according%20to%20Angeles%20National%20Forest%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Everyone%20panicked'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20erupted%20midmorning%20and%20swelled%20quickly%2C%20taking%20many%20residents%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20man%2C%20who%20gave%20his%20name%20as%20Gary%2C%20told%20broadcaster%20KTLA%20hot%20ashes%20were%20raining%20down%20on%20his%20community%20of%20Sea%20Ridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20smoke%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20and%20I%20was%20assured%20that%20it%20would%20not%20come%20over%20the%20hill...%20Five%20minutes%20later%2C%20it's%20coming%20down%20the%20hill%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20panicked%2C%20that's%20when%20everybody%20made%20a%20run%20and%20went%20to%20go%20and%20pack%20their%20houses%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvacuee%20Kelsey%20Trainor%20said%20she%20saw%20the%20fire%20explode%20in%20size%20as%20she%20was%20fleeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20time%20we%20got%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20hill%2C%20which%20is%20about%20two%20or%20three%20miles%2C%20there%20were%20flames%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20road%2C%20and%20it%20became%20gridlocked%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20knew%20what%20to%20do.%20Everyone%20was%20honking%20their%20horns.%20There's%20flames%20all%20around%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20see%20people%20walking%20with%20suitcases%2C%20with%20their%20dogs%2C%20children.%20An%20elderly%20woman%20was%20really%20visibly%20upset%20and%20in%20tears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacific%20Palisades%20resident%20Andrew%20Hires%20told%20AFP%20he%20got%20a%20text%20alerting%20him%20to%20the%20fire%20as%20his%20child%20was%20at%20the%20dentist%20about%20to%20have%20a%20tooth%20extracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20pulled%20off%20the%20mask%20and%20ran%20to%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20rough%20night'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20came%20as%20the%20area%20was%20being%20hit%20by%20seasonal%20Santa%