%20never%20doing%20it%20again%20understands%20the%20feeling%20the%20fashion%20capital%20of%20Italy%20is%20heavy%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItaly%20hadn't%20hopped%20on%20the%20healthy%20bandwagon%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20which%20saw%20dramatic%20declines%20in%20the%20smoking%20habits%20of%20younger%20adults%20in%20the%20US%20and%20many%20other%20countries.%20According%20to%20a%20cross-sectional%20study%20conducted%20by%20National%20Health%20Interview%20Surveys%20between%202011%20and%202022%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%E2%80%9CAdults%20younger%20than%2040%20years%20had%20dramatic%20declines%20in%20smoking%20prevalence%20during%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20especially%20among%20those%20with%20higher%20incomes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20Ban%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilan's%20reasons%20for%20imposing%20a%20strict%20ban%20on%20smoking%20in%20public%20spaces%20are%20rooted%20in%20the%20city's%20effort%20to%20tackle%20air%20pollution.%20The%20city%20council%20sees%20smoking%20as%20a%20significant%20pollutant%3A%20cigarettes%20are%20responsible%20for%207%25%20of%20total%20emissions%20in%20Milan%20and%20its%20suburbs.%20Given%20that%20almost%20a%20quarter%20of%20Italy's%20population%20smokes%2C%20this%20doesn't%20seem%20outlandish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enforceability%20of%20this%20ban%20can%20be%20debated.%20And%20so%20can%20the%20compulsions%20behind%20it.%20Do%20human%20beings%20invariably%20make%20the%20best%20decisions%20for%20themselves%3F%20Rarely%20are%20smokers%20unaware%20of%20the%20dangers%20they%20subject%20themselves%20to%20with%20each%20puff.%20But%20rarely%20is%20this%20awareness%20enough%20to%20quit.%20The%20gross%20realism%20of%20graphics%20on%20cigarette%20packs%20is%20no%20deterrent%20either.%20Smoking-attributable%20diseases%20and%20death%20happen%20only%20to%20other%20people%2C%20not%20us%E2%80%94such%20is%20the%20smokers'%20sense%20of%20invincibility.%20Each%20year%2C%20about%207%20million%20people%20die%20of%20smoking-related%20health%20complications%20globally.%20But%2C%20they%20are%20some%20other%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20first%20week%20of%20the%20new%20year%20ends%2C%20evaluation%20of%20all%20those%20zealously%20formulated%20resolutions%20also%20creeps%20in.%20In%20a%202015%20study%20conducted%20in%20the%20US%2C%20about%2068%25%20of%20smokers%20expressed%20a%20wish%20to%20quit.%20Many%20manage%20to%20quit%2C%20some%20do%20not.%20Every%20January%2C%20the%20Potential%20Quitters%20Club%20regroups%20and%20realigns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Smoking%20Was%20The%20'Sexiest'%20Thing%20Around%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20smokers%20complain%20of%20being%20discriminated%20against%20for%20being%20banished%20to%20secluded%20spaces.%20Those%20old%20enough%20to%20remember%20the%20days%20when%20you%20could%20smoke%20on%20a%20flight%20rue%20the%20slow%20decline%20of%20human%20civilisation.%20Literature%20and%20visual%20pop%20culture%20are%20replete%20with%20references%20to%20a%20golden%20era%20of%20smoking.%20When%20mothers%20could%20smoke%20with%20babies%20on%20their%20laps.%20When%20nothing%20of%20note%20could%20be%20done%20without%20chainsmoking.%20Smoking%20was%20once%20marketed%20as%20the%20sexiest%20thing%20around%3B%20the%20smoker%20was%20a%20rebel%2C%20a%20genius.%20Self-portraits%20of%20Van%20Gogh%20and%20Edward%20Munch%20with%20cigarettes%20were%20great%20advertisements%20for%20the%20latter.%20Smoking%20women%20were%20a%20league%20ahead%20because%20they%20smashed%20patriarchal%20rules%20of%20propriety%20quite%20literally%20blow%20by%20blow.%20Heck%2C%20even%20gods%20smoked.%20Or%2C%20so%20did%20we%20believe%20and%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20Depictions%20of%20gods%20smoking%20in%20the%20Mayan%20art%20is%20an%20example%20of%20how%20man%20creates%20god%20in%20his%20image%20and%20not%20vice%20versa.%20Maya%20people%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20heavy%20smokers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadlines%20around%20the%20Milan%20smoking%20ban%20have%20underscored%20the%20paradoxical%20association%20of%20smoking%20with%20style.%20According%20to%20the%20WHO%20data%20on%20smoking%2C%2080%25%20of%20global%20smokers%20are%20from%20low%20and%20middle-income%20countries.%20Smoking%20prevalence%20in%20the%20lowest-income%20groups%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20the%20highest%20survey%20after%20survey.%20Smoking's%20traditional%20ties%20with%20making%20style%20statements%20in%20the%20world%20of%20the%20wealthy%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20been%20a%20bit%20odd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20Milan%20ban%2C%20after%20all%2C%20the%20assertion%20of%20the%20elite%3F%20By%20making%20the%20fashionable%20streets%20of%20the%20city%20smoke-free%2C%20a%20signal%20is%20being%20sent.%20Enough%20of%20slumming%20it%20out%3B%20we%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20our%20lane%20by%20being%20healthy%20now.%20Killing%20oneself%20slowly%20is%20not%20stylish%20anymore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20banning%20something%20stops%20its%20proliferation%20is%20another%20debate.%20What%20they%20do%20achieve%20is%20the%20destruction%20of%20agency.%20And%20that's%20what%20Milan's%20city%20council%20seems%20to%20be%20going%20for.%20Just%20because%20you%20think%20you%20should%20light%20up%20one%20and%20subject%20everyone%20else%20in%20your%20vicinity%20to%20passive%20smoke%20is%20not%20a%20good%20enough%20reason%20anymore.%20It's%20not%20your%20choice%20anymore.%20Should%20it%20ever%20have%20been%20a%20choice%20is%20a%20pertinent%20question%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20is%20your%20New%20Year's%20resolution%20of%20quitting%20smoking%20going%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736325720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhmn02m0o_smoking_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%2