.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-1200x1600.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3780_11zon-1735049817.jpg%201805w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EForeka%20aims%20to%20train%20women%20farmers%20so%20they%20can%20help%20increase%20the%20sales%20of%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20running%20a%20large-scale%20venture%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20traders%20felt%20threatened%20by%20our%20model.%20They%20were%20used%20to%20controlling%20the%20market%2C%20but%20we%20believed%20in%20the%20power%20of%20direct%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Despite%20their%20venture%20causing%20some%20tension%20in%20the%20local%20markets%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20pressed%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20the%20young%20entrepreneur%20realised%20that%20offering%20higher%20incentives%20to%20farmers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20sustain%20long-term%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20became%20increasingly%20seasonal%2C%20with%20supply%20chain%20challenges%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20operations.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20our%20operations%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20expand%20our%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20cold-pressed%20oil%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20noticed%20an%20increasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20insight%20led%20them%20to%20pivot%20their%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20team%20ventured%20into%20the%20cold-pressed%20oil%20market%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Foreka%20in%20Rajasthan.%20This%20expansion%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20support%20Satyam%20received%20in%20November%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20fellowship%20from%20The%20Buddha%20Institute%2C%20founded%20by%20Ved%20Arya%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Buddha%20Institute%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20generous%20grant%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20which%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20enabling%20the%20team%20to%20scale%20their%20operations.%20Their%20research%20into%20the%20region%20highlighted%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20outmigration%2C%20presenting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20local%20employment.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20mustard%20seeds%20in%20the%20area%20made%20it%20an%20ideal%20location%20for%20their%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20NGOs%20like%20SRIJAN%20to%20establish%20a%20value%20chain%20for%20farming%2C%20offering%20farmers%20better%20prices%20and%20resources%20to%20test%20seed%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20supporting%20farmers%20directly%2C%20we%20ensured%20fair%20prices%20and%20sustainable%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%20The%20setup%20includes%20cold-pressed%20machines%20owned%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%20while%20Foreka%20works%20on%20a%20co-profit%20model%2C%20sharing%2050%25%20of%20the%20profits%20after%20covering%20costs.%20Partnering%20with%20two%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%2C%20one%20near%20Jhansi%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20Chambal%20Valley%2C%20Foreka%20sources%20groundnuts%2C%20processes%20them%2C%20and%20sells%20groundnut%20oil.%20The%20model%20helps%20reduce%20outmigration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20local%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20oil%20processing%20unit%20and%20office%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523.jpg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-2048x1536.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_0329-1_11zon-1735049523-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392177%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221805%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20given%20me%20financial%20stability%2C%20pride%20in%20my%20work%2C%20and%20a%20brighter%20future%20for%20my%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramavtar%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20farmer.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20farmer%20with%20divided%20land%20and%20unpredictable%20income%2C%20life%20was%20tough.%20I%20struggled%20to%20provide%20for%20my%20family%20and%20lacked%20opportunities%20for%20my%20children.%20But%20joining%20Foreka%20changed%20everything.%20They%20offered%20fair%20prices%20for%20my%20mustard%20seeds%2C%20which%20boosted%20my%20income%2C%20and%20trained%20me%20to%20operate%20machines%2C%20giving%20me%20a%20steady%20job.%20Now%2C%20my%20children%20are%20receiving%20an%20education%2C%20and%20one%20is%20pursuing%20a%20degree%20in%20Veterinary%20Sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20treated%20as%20partners%2C%20not%20just%20suppliers.%20They%20have%20a%20direct%20stake%20in%20the%20success%20of%20the%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20ensures%20that%20they%20are%20as%20invested%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20business%20as%20we%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%2C%20building%20a%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20significant%20challenges%20as%20they%20expanded%20their%20business.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20difficult%20to%20raise%20funds%20after%20becoming%20a%20private%20limited%20company.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20impact%20investors%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20entrepreneurship%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20their%20inexperience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20driven%20by%20willpower%2C%20but%20we%20had%20little%20experience%20and%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20skills.%20We%20realised%20that%20skills%20are%20developed%20through%20experience.%20So%2C%20we%20took%20the%20time%20to%20seek%20mentoring%20in%20areas%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20and%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20major%20challenge%20came%20when%20the%20trio%20encountered%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20fraud%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20taken%20a%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20loan%20to%20procure%20oil%20from%20farmers%2C%20and%20we%20received%20our%20first%20order%20in%20July%202022%2C%20a%20300-litre%20batch%20of%20cold-pressed%20oil.%20The%20order%20was%20valued%20around%20Rs%206-7%20lakh%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20send%20it%20to%20Noida%20in%20the%20NCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20all%20night%20packing%20and%20preparing%20the%20shipment%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20collect%20the%20payment.%20The%20vendor%20told%20me%20that%20his%20bank%20account%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20working%20and%20that%20he%20could%20only%20transfer%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20initially%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20was%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20troubles.%20The%20vendor%20ended%20up%20not%20paying%20the%20remaining%20Rs%204%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20huge%20challenge.%20To%20repay%20the%20loan%2C%20we%20had%20to%20raise%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20from%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20difficulties%20but%20also%20being%20grateful%20for%20the%20support%20he%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201774px)%20100vw%2C%201774px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221774%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20friends%20at%20a%20pop-up%20store%20of%20their%20brand%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437.jpg%201774w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG_3093-2_11zon-1-1735050437-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20black%20mustard%20cold-pressed%20oil%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20320%20and%20the%20yellow%20mustard%20oil%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20450%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20setbacks%2C%20the%20trio%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20never%20wavered.%20They%20knew%20that%20these%20challenges%20were%20part%20of%20the%20journey%20and%20continued%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20the%20support%20of%20their%20team%2C%20mentors%2C%20and%20the%20community%20they%20were%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeka%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363795%2Fnutmeg-export-from-india-farmers-pollachi-village-tamil-nadu-middlemen-fpc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevenue%20surged%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20in%202023-24%20to%20Rs%201.3%20crore%20in%20the%20first%20two%20quarters%20of%202024-25.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024-25%2C%20marking%20a%20more%20than%20fourfold%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20cold-pressed%20oils%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20320%20per%20litre%20for%20black%20mustard%2C%20Rs%20450%20for%20yellow%20mustard%2C%20and%20Rs%20500%20for%20groundnut%2C%20are%20gently%20extracted%20using%20the%20cold-press%20method%2C%20preserving%20their%20full%20nutritional%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Foreka%20plans%20to%20expand%20further%20by%20establishing%20processing%20units%20for%20five%20oilseeds%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20involving%2010%2C000%20farmers%2C%20and%20creating%20250%20jobs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20developing%20a%20%E2%80%98House%20of%20Mustard%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20project%20focused%20on%20value-added%20mustard%20products%20such%20as%20mustard%20sauce%20and%20chutney.%20Currently%20in%20the%20R%26amp%3BD%20stage%2C%20the%20initiative%20has